         <div type="translation">
            <p>
               <choice corresp="#a1">
                  <seg><seg type="prim_transl">[TB] for the ordinary, desires are not easy to keep away. [SKT] Truly (the very variegated royal chariots) get old.</seg></seg>
               </choice>
               <choice corresp="#a2">
                  <seg><seg type="prim_transl">[TB] (and likewise the body) reaches old age. [SKT] but the law of the virtuous does not reach old age</seg></seg>
               </choice>
               <choice corresp="#a3">
                  <seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:peyrot2013b"/><citedRange>309</citedRange></bibl></seg>
                  <seg><seg type="prim_transl">[SKT] Shame be upon you, vulgar old age! [TB] Shame be upon you, vulgar old age!</seg></seg>
               </choice>
               <choice corresp="#a3 ">
